                            <p class="mt-2 text-muted fw-bold">正在分析美股基本面數據並進行評分篩選...</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="table-responsive" id="us-master-table-wrap" style="display:none;">
                            <table class="table table-hover table-striped mb-0 align-middle">
                                <thead class="table-light">
